             05  wc-lastname          PIC  x(40) VALUE space.
             05  wc-user-email        PIC  x(40) VALUE space.
             05  wc-user-phonenumber  PIC  x(40) VALUE space.
             05  wc-user-username     PIC  x(40) VALUE space.
             05  wc-user-password     PIC  x(40) VALUE space.
